吃的話，隨時都可以交給我喔～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf_right01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"area4832-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"我也要我也要！　紫紫願意找我的話，\n我會馬上飛過去喔～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"area4832-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"筑紫","body":"真是的～，你們只是想吃甜點才這樣說吧？\n不過謝謝你們，我就聽你們的，拜託你們來幫忙吧！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"area4832-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"你打算做什麼樣的南瓜甜點呢？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"area4832-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"筑紫","body":"總之，我想把這個會場裡有的全部都做一次看看！\n之後還有……大家，有什麼想委託我的嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"area4832-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"我想要\n跟那邊的傑克．南瓜燈一樣大的甜點！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf_left01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"area4832-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":26}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"欸……那邊的是指……\n大小幾乎跟我們一樣大了吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nnf_left01","expressionName":"surprised01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"area4832-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"所以，這樣子才有震撼力啊！\n小白你不懂呢～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"area4832-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"w